## Fuentes de componentes — en orden de prioridad

### 1. shadcn/ui
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add accordion alert avatar badge button card
npx shadcn@latest add checkbox dialog dropdown-menu form input
npx shadcn@latest add label popover progress select separator
npx shadcn@latest add sheet skeleton switch table tabs textarea
npx shadcn@latest add toast tooltip
```

### 2. Magic UI
```
Texto:    BlurFade, AnimatedGradientText, TypingAnimation, WordFadeIn
Fondos:   DotPattern, GridPattern, Meteors, Particles
Botones:  ShimmerButton, RippleButton, InteractiveHoverButton
Cards:    MagicCard, BentoGrid, BentoCard
Números:  NumberTicker, AnimatedCircularProgressBar
Layout:   Marquee
```

### 3. Custom
Solo si shadcn + Magic UI no cubren. → `src/components/[feature]/`

